---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="border-t border-slate-800/60 bg-[#070b14]">
  <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-3xl px-4 py-10">
    <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-100">How Kainoa works</h2>
    <p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-slate-400">
      Kainoa has three brains: <strong class="text-slate-200">Kainoa</strong> answers instantly from your <code class="text-slate-300">responses.json</code>. <strong class="text-slate-200">Forum</strong> searches your local <code class="text-slate-300">forum-index.json</code>. <strong class="text-slate-200">AI</strong> runs Phi-3.5 in your browser — nothing leaves your device.
    </p>

    <h3 class="mb-2 mt-8 text-base font-semibold text-slate-100">Powered by</h3>
    <ul class="space-y-1 text-[15px] text-slate-400">
      <li>• WebLLM + MLC (local AI)</li>
      <li>• forum.theeastpacific.com</li>
      <li>• 100% client-side</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="mb-3 mt-8 text-base font-semibold text-slate-100">TEP Links</h3>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-[15px] text-slate-300">
      <a href="https://forum.theeastpacific.com" class="hover:text-cyan-400">Forum</a>
      <a href="https://www.nationstates.net/region=the_east_pacific" class="hover:text-cyan-400">Region</a>
      <a href="#" class="hover:text-cyan-400">Discord</a>
      <a href="#" class="hover:text-cyan-400">Wiki</a>
      <a href="#" class="hover:text-cyan-400">Concordat</a>
      <a href="https://forum.theeastpacific.com/t/citizenship-application" class="hover:text-cyan-400">Apply</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="border-t border-slate-800/60 py-5 text-center text-xs text-slate-500">
    Kainoa v1.1 • Built for The East Pacific • © {year}
  </div>
</footer>